OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1781553960
OL,3,CTeenager pleads guilty to violent
OL,4,Cdisorder by throwing bottle at police
OL,6,FAn 18-year-old man has pleaded guilty
OL,7,Fto violent disorder by throwing a
OL,8,Fbottle at police during a protest in
OL,9,FSouthampton.
OL,11,FCallum Cool, who was 17 at the time of
OL,12,Fthe demonstration following the murder
OL,13,Fof Henry Nowak ` which took place on
OL,14,FJune 2, entered his plea during a
OL,15,Fhearing at Southampton Magistrates'
OL,16,FCourt.
OL,18,FThe teenager, of Robinia Green,
OL,19,FSouthampton, was granted conditional
OL,20,Fbail to appear at Southampton Crown
OL,21,FCourt for sentencing on June 29.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
