OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1781553960
OL,3,CTeenager pleads guilty to violent
OL,4,Cdisorder by throwing bottle at police
OL,6,FDistrict Judge Robinson told him: "I
OL,7,Fam going to list your case for
OL,8,FSouthampton Crown Court for sentence
OL,9,Fwhere the next hearing will take place
OL,10,Fon June 29.
OL,12,F"I am prepared to grant you
OL,13,Fconditional bail which means you must
OL,14,Fturn up on June 29 or you may be
OL,15,Fcommitting another offence."
OL,26,@nD@cOUtD@AOUwD@\O]
