PN,38803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1781553960
OL,3,CTeenager pleads guilty to violent
OL,4,Cdisorder by throwing bottle at police
OL,6,FThe district judge set conditions that
OL,7,FCool would be fitted with an
OL,8,Felectronic tag, with a curfew at his
OL,9,Fhome and ordered him not to attend any
OL,10,Fprotest or gathering of more than 10
OL,11,Fpeople.
OL,13,FThe June 2 demonstration involving
OL,14,F1,000 people started outside
OL,15,FSouthampton Central Police Station
OL,16,Fbefore hundreds moved on to the
OL,17,FPortswood area where Mr Nowak had been
OL,18,Fkilled and where the violence started.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
