FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1781553960
OL,3,CTeenager pleads guilty to violent
OL,4,Cdisorder by throwing bottle at police
OL,6,FCool is the 23rd person to be charged
OL,7,Fover the protest, with 13 people
OL,8,Fhaving been jailed so far.
OL,10,FAnger had erupted after police body-
OL,11,Fworn video was released showing Mr
OL,12,FNowak being placed in handcuffs
OL,13,Fmoments before he became unconscious
OL,14,Fand subsequently died.
OL,16,FVickrum Digwa, 23, who lived in a
OL,17,Fnearby road with his family, was
OL,18,Fjailed for life to serve a minimum of
OL,19,F21 years for his murder.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/4
